# ============================================================
# AI Usage Tracker — Environment Variables
# ============================================================
# Most tools work with ZERO configuration:
#
#   Claude Code  →  reads ~/.claude/projects/**/*.jsonl
#   Codex CLI    →  reads ~/.codex/sessions/**/*.jsonl
#   Copilot      →  reads your `gh` CLI session (run `gh auth login` once)
#
# Only fill in the variables below if you need them.
# ============================================================

# --- GitHub Copilot (Org/Enterprise) ---
# Only needed if you're an org admin with Copilot Business/Enterprise.
# Personal Copilot is tracked automatically via `gh auth token`.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
# GITHUB_ORG=your-org-name

# --- Cursor ---
# Enterprise teams only. Get your API key from Cursor team settings.
# CURSOR_API_KEY=

# --- App Settings ---
# CACHE_TTL_MINUTES=5
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
